ning mindset","Small bet eng-led culture"],"ai_era_implications":["Playbook half-life measured in months not years"]},{"pattern_name":"PM/design squeeze from engineering velocity","source_episode":"Anthropic's $1B to $19B growth run: how Claude became the fastest-growing AI product in history | Amol Avasare","source_guest":"Amol Avasare","source_quote_or_context":"Engineering moving so fast PM and design become bottlenecks if not adapted.","category":"Org Dynamics","core_belief":"When eng ships daily, traditional PM/design cadences break.","operational_pattern":"Resize PM/design for integrator and quality roles; let eng own micro-ships; PM on >2-week and cross-functional.","organizational_archetype":"Fast-shipping AI product org","hidden_assumptions":["Design quality may suffer without bottleneck","Not all eng has taste"],"pressure_scenarios":["Daily launches","Enterprise quality bar","OpenClaw-scale events"],"failure_modes":["Design dept overwhelmed","PMs irrelevant","UX inconsistency"],"contradictions":["Wants more PMs eventually while minimizing now"],"behavioral_signals":["Eng ships without design on small bets","PM on Cowork-scale launches"],"emotional_political_dynamics":["Design/PM fear of irrelevance"],"operational_adaptations":["Integrator PM model","Design on high-impact surfaces only"],"ai_era_implications":["Eng velocity from AI widens PM/design bottleneck"]},{"pattern_name":"Nov 2025 coding inflection point","source_episode":"An AI state of the union: We've passed the inflection point, dark factories are coming, and automation timelines | Simon Willison","source_guest":"Simon Willison","source_quote_or_context":"We've passed the inflection point\u2014professional coding changed fundamentally around late 2025.","category":"Industry Shift","core_belief":"AI coding crossed from assistive to agentic for professionals.","operational_pattern":"Retrain engineering orgs for agentic workflows; treat pre-inflection playbooks as obsolete.","organizational_archetyp